<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1437,509,966]" pageId="14" pageNumber="568">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,214,509,534]" pageId="14" pageNumber="568">Note.</emphasis>
The 
<typeStatus box="[270,368,509,534]" pageId="14" pageNumber="568">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authority="F. Morawitz, 1893" authorityName="F. Morawitz" authorityYear="1893" box="[405,854,509,534]" class="Insecta" family="Sphecidae" genus="Ammophila" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirticeps">
<emphasis box="[405,639,509,533]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="568">Ammophila hirticeps</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Morawitz" box="[645,854,509,534]" pageId="14" pageNumber="568" refString="Morawitz, F. (1893) Catalog der von D. Glasunov in Turkestan gesammelten Hymenoptera Fossoria. Horae Societatis Entomologicae Rossicae, 27, 391 - 428." type="journal article" year="1893">F. Morawitz, 1893</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, described from 
<collectingCountry box="[1039,1149,509,534]" name="Tajikistan" pageId="14" pageNumber="568">Tajikistan</collectingCountry>
and synonymized with 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Dollfuss, 2010 b:" authorityYear="1249" class="Insecta" family="Sphecidae" genus="Podalonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="andrei">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="568">P. andrei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[292,359,545,570]" name="China" pageId="14" pageNumber="568">China</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[415,524,545,570]" name="Mongolia" pageId="14" pageNumber="568">Mongolia</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Dollfuss" box="[567,761,545,570]" pageId="14" pageNumber="568" refString="Dollfuss, H. (2010 b) A key to wasps of the genus Podalonia Fernald 1927 (Hymenoptera: Apoidea: Sphecidae) of the Old World. Linzer Biologische Beitrage, 42, 1241 - 1291." type="journal article" year="2010" yearSuffix="b">Dollfuss (2010b)</bibRefCitation>
, clearly differs from the male of 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Dollfuss, 2010 b:" authorityYear="1249" box="[1134,1234,545,569]" class="Insecta" family="Sphecidae" genus="Podalonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="andrei">
<emphasis box="[1134,1234,545,569]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="568">P. andrei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; it was labeled as “ 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Dollfuss, 2010 b:" authorityYear="1249" box="[163,235,581,605]" class="Insecta" family="Sphecidae" genus="Podalonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="andrei">
<emphasis box="[163,235,581,605]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="568">andrei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” by H. Dollfuss. Consequently, 
<taxonomicName authority="(Dalla Torre, 1897)" authorityName=": Bohart &amp; Menke" authorityYear="1976" baseAuthorityName="Dalla Torre" baseAuthorityYear="1897" box="[627,1137,581,606]" class="Insecta" family="Sphecidae" genus="Podalonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="turcestanica">
<emphasis box="[627,894,581,605]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="568">Podalonia turcestanica</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Dalla" box="[914,1129,581,606]" pageId="14" pageNumber="568" refString="von Dalla Torre, K. W. (1897) Catalogus Hymenopterorum hucusque descriptorum systematicus et synonymicus, Volumen VIII: Fossores (Sphegidae). Guilelmi Engelmann, Lipsiae, 749 pp." type="book" year="1897">Dalla Torre, 1897</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, its valid name, must be resurrected from synonymy.
</paragraph>
